Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.92,0:01:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是擁有地球最大礦物資源的\N馬·克貝大佐的根據地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.99,0:01:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球聯邦軍正準備著進攻這基地的敖德薩計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.07,0:01:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,White Base為了參加這一作戰而向西行進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.44,0:02:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而蘭巴·拉爾的進攻仍然沒有停息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.73,0:02:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,『深刻憎恨的激鬥』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.13,0:02:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有這些殘舊的ZAKU和4台坦克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.50,0:02:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明顯地上校根本就不想幫我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.41,0:02:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靠你了，達智中尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.35,0:02:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論如何也要為蘭巴復仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.35,0:02:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的心情也和哈蒙小姐一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.20,0:03:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.47,0:03:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是達智中尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.60,0:03:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去偵察的人回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.91,0:03:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.07,0:03:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.24,0:03:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,木馬現在背山駐紮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.71,0:03:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以從那方面進攻呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.75,0:03:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.58,0:03:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,木馬損壞程度如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.62,0:03:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們正拚命修理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.38,0:03:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎人手不足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.62,0:03:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那該去準備，要盡快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.52,0:03:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！哈蒙小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.64,0:03:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,損壞相當嚴重！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.54,0:03:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若再受攻擊便完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.41,0:03:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且零件快用盡了\N武器也用盡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.68,0:03:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想法子補給是支持不了多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.19,0:04:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別發嚕唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.39,0:04:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在前線是不知會發生甚麼事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.69,0:04:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用頭腦和努力補救吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.02,0:04:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,頭腦嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.03,0:04:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅又如何呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.90,0:04:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別提他了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.27,0:04:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你覺得好點嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.44,0:04:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒大礙了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.77,0:04:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良，你好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.41,0:04:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良，你好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.51,0:04:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身體怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.55,0:04:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.24,0:04:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.38,0:04:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.28,0:04:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅所製造的哈囉很好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.45,0:04:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是說真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.04,0:04:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈囉很好的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.87,0:04:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良！你快康復吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.62,0:04:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很多謝你，哈囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.13,0:04:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到你那麼會說話！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.08,0:04:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有事可讓我效勞？良
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.13,0:04:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒...沒有！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.74,0:04:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以告訴大家我沒事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.17,0:04:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請他們別擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.94,0:04:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說隊長又將阿姆羅困入窖內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.24,0:04:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.44,0:04:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅還是這麼硬頸嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.08,0:05:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長也真是的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.09,0:05:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們在運輸車裝上重型坦克了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.09,0:05:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加多兩個引擎便可加快速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.59,0:05:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZAKU則換上坦克主力炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.43,0:05:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們共有2台戰車，16名士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.90,0:05:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部也是由蘭巴上尉所訓練的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.94,0:05:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備非常周到！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.07,0:05:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了卡爾瑪的仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.24,0:05:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們才來地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.91,0:05:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但任務還未成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.71,0:05:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然敵軍數目少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.88,0:05:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但始終也是聯邦軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.08,0:05:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新銳主力戰艦及機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.92,0:05:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION內的人民都對我們抱有期望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.16,0:05:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對我來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.62,0:05:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭巴是個誠懇和勇敢的軍官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.79,0:05:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亦是我所傾心的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.26,0:05:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了我所傾心的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.73,0:05:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算死在沙漠也在所不惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.73,0:05:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在有誰願意參加今次行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.47,0:05:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相信蘭巴也不會勉強大家的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.67,0:05:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不會！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.04,0:06:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈蒙小姐，妳放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.01,0:06:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家已有必死決心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.41,0:06:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝大家！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.01,0:06:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杜路加，拜託了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.25,0:06:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！哈蒙小姐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.55,0:06:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海，靠你了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.45,0:06:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！哈蒙小姐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.79,0:06:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,路遜，你要加油！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.02,0:06:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！我一定要報仇！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.20,0:06:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.37,0:06:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別動！否則傷口又爆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.37,0:06:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不動的話傷口更難埋口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.95,0:06:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你覺得如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.05,0:06:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想談談阿姆羅的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.62,0:06:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 我是不可放他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.08,0:06:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若給他知道我們對他有期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.29,0:06:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅會愈來愈自高自大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.22,0:06:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相信阿姆羅不會的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.96,0:06:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎？米萊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.26,0:06:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的！但這關乎軍法...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.53,0:06:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是野生動物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.73,0:06:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放入籠也會明白自己的立場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.33,0:06:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的意思是要等阿姆羅自己反省？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.23,0:07:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這有點強辯哦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.10,0:07:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說我強辯？為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.04,0:07:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為人類有語言溝通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.01,0:07:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁我還有氣力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.51,0:07:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良，別再說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.68,0:07:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布萊特，你也未好好和阿姆羅談過吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.11,0:07:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然這樣老虎又怎會聽話呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.22,0:07:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快叫雪拉來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.19,0:07:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先扶良入房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.35,0:07:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.04,0:07:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果那男孩又來妨礙我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.74,0:07:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭巴，請你保佑我們！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.18,0:07:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成了，只要再調整一下磁氣壓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.13,0:08:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是駕駛員 睡眠也是職責之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.78,0:08:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰在外面？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.34,0:08:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅？你未睡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.35,0:08:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是良？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.68,0:08:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弄醒你不好意思...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.38,0:08:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你傷勢如何！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.18,0:08:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不用擔心我的，阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.12,0:08:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長又鎖起你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.09,0:08:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你很不滿嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.69,0:08:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.13,0:08:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白隊長的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.93,0:08:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒不滿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.46,0:08:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這樣想就好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.13,0:08:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長還說你是一隻野生的老虎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.57,0:08:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他似乎很害怕你呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.17,0:08:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是否覺得好笑！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.71,0:08:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說我是...野生老虎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.04,0:08:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，我完全信任你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.48,0:08:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.01,0:08:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這點傷，不怕的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.16,0:09:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良，你為什麼還四處去？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.99,0:09:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芙勞·波，他在這邊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.66,0:09:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來他來找阿姆羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.67,0:09:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.53,0:09:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉！良沒事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.54,0:09:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他沒事，不用擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.58,0:09:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這辦法很實際
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.08,0:09:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是古代流傳下來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.82,0:09:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最完美的攻擊方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.92,0:09:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第1隊攻擊隊在敵人防禦力較弱的部份開始進攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.79,0:09:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其它部份可以不理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.56,0:09:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要集中一點就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.46,0:09:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然武器性能上他們佔優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.53,0:09:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但以這方法必將木馬攻陷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.37,0:09:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始了，木馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.21,0:10:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人嗎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.98,0:10:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了！敵軍從後面來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.99,0:10:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵襲！哪有這麼多？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.09,0:10:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不怕你的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.40,0:10:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只用一架ZAKU就想來攻母艦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.17,0:10:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是不自量力！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.74,0:10:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佐保，可以加快速度嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.41,0:10:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自從上次被破壞後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.08,0:10:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還未完全修好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.45,0:10:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.22,0:10:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是只得一台ZAKU嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.69,0:10:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不...不得了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.43,0:10:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,旋轉軸壞了！引擎雖然在動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.36,0:10:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人！有方法嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.83,0:10:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,方法？哪有方法掩護他們？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.97,0:11:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良，你要振作！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.97,0:11:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別理我 先放阿姆羅出來再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.51,0:11:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切後果由我負責
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.05,0:11:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.31,0:11:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但你先要返回床上休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.22,0:11:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會的了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.42,0:11:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.21,0:11:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉妳在哪裏？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.32,0:11:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快回艦橋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.76,0:11:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以告訴我阿姆羅倉房的密碼嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.33,0:11:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.00,0:11:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是良說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.00,0:11:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說要放阿姆羅出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.67,0:11:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後果由他承擔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.24,0:11:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真多管閒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.67,0:11:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也願意承擔後果，告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.37,0:11:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是F─36號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.68,0:11:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是良為你求情的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.22,0:11:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你要加倍努力呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.02,0:11:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.02,0:11:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我立即去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.22,0:11:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太可惡了！欺人太甚！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.96,0:11:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有伏兵？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.04,0:12:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這方法真行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.37,0:12:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,木馬現在不能動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.34,0:12:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要你見識蘭巴部隊的利害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.00,0:12:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長1、2、3號已...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.34,0:12:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先別管這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.90,0:12:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,起飛吧！米萊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.21,0:12:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.37,0:12:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉，GUNDAM可以出動了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.68,0:12:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！應該沒有問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.35,0:12:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,GUNDAM可以出發了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.35,0:12:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為修理的人受了傷，修理...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.08,0:12:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以動便成！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.45,0:12:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.55,0:12:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之我先用核戰機出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.05,0:12:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,修理中所以未和GUNDAM連接
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.92,0:12:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了，阿姆羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.16,0:13:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,母艦現正要發動呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.49,0:13:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以嗎，阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.90,0:13:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.70,0:13:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長，核戰機現在出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.43,0:13:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.43,0:13:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算不可以也要可以吧，雪拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.57,0:13:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.37,0:13:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不出動GUNDAM的話根本無法應付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.05,0:13:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！哥哥們的墳墓不理了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.92,0:13:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會怕你的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.09,0:13:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我如今已不同了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.96,0:13:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會後退的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.40,0:13:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你只要發射GUNDAM零件出去便成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.44,0:13:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然說明書有寫上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.94,0:13:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但未試過呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.51,0:13:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在母艦誰也一樣！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.08,0:13:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到時我會再想方法的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.08,0:13:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道，我盡力做吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.05,0:13:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是正規軍竟然會這樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.25,0:13:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,核戰機，出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.40,0:14:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會讓你們接近母艦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.27,0:14:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芙勞·波，你去幫助他們吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.07,0:14:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在右手面的機鎗位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.44,0:14:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳應該懂得使用吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.26,0:14:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.14,0:14:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,記著戴上鋼盔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.54,0:14:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否則會震聾耳朵的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.49,0:14:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.05,0:14:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坦克故障了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.55,0:14:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米萊，母艦還不能動嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.92,0:14:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,引擎被炸壞了，所以失去了浮力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.76,0:14:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要發射GUNDAM零件出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.06,0:14:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是由阿姆羅提議的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.63,0:14:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良，你別動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.90,0:14:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的傷勢最重的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.73,0:14:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若母艦被毀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.57,0:14:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算沒病也一樣要死呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.14,0:14:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是...這我也明白！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.48,0:15:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良，你究竟想做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.35,0:15:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要駕駛坦克...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.42,0:15:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果母艦不是動不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.05,0:15:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也沒這麼易出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.40,0:15:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好不容易擊毀一架！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.37,0:15:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我出擊得太遲了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.74,0:15:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，可以發射GUNDAM零件了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.47,0:15:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,動手吧！戰機的子彈也用盡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.24,0:15:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,GUNDAM B零件，發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.62,0:15:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,激光頻道符合 核戰機變換
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.49,0:15:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接合激光電波，180度回轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.57,0:15:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,情況良好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.37,0:15:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.91,0:16:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安城，請發射A部份零件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.14,0:16:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道，裝上發射位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.68,0:16:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅準備了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.68,0:16:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道，做得相當好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.04,0:16:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.28,0:16:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算可瞄準他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.51,0:16:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但這也會傷及母艦的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.21,0:16:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有埋身肉博了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.26,0:16:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等！他們想用戰車撞向母艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.00,0:17:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裏面是裝滿炸彈嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.67,0:17:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不成！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.81,0:17:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然想阻擋戰車！別妄想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.22,0:17:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,單憑GUNDAM一個是阻不了我們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.02,0:17:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撞上木馬的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.59,0:17:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裏面的炸藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.03,0:17:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,達智，你去後面對付GUNDAM
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.70,0:17:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！哈蒙小姐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.08,0:17:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在上面！看我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.33,0:18:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,GUNDAM竟然同時收拾兩方面的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.43,0:18:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我看中的人果然有點本領
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.33,0:18:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.44,0:18:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今次糟了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.01,0:18:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要開炮？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.67,0:18:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能只射中重戰車吧 有可能誤中GUNDAM的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.78,0:18:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算GUNDAM的裝甲有多厚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.12,0:18:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也抵擋不住近距離攻擊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.52,0:18:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且GUNDAM和炸藥的爆炸力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.69,0:18:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會連母艦也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.03,0:18:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是哈蒙小姐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.46,0:18:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本來我是很喜歡你的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.70,0:18:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小伙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.04,0:18:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今次我可以成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.81,0:18:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.32,0:18:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.42,0:18:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.69,0:19:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快些！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.66,0:19:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,核...核戰機？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.49,0:19:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.20,0:19:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯！只要破壞它一邊的引擎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.90,0:19:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就可以了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.13,0:19:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看著吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.34,0:19:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.38,0:19:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.43,0:19:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有敵人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.70,0:19:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經結束戰爭了，阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.36,0:19:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,GUNDAM呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.61,0:19:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒事吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.37,0:19:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒事，核戰機裏面的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.94,0:19:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.37,0:19:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你聽了後別難過，阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.68,0:19:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是良
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.54,0:20:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良撞過去的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.32,0:20:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是良
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.05,0:20:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳騙我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.65,0:20:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良已受了重傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.05,0:20:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒可能去應戰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.09,0:20:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳...妳別胡說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.67,0:20:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我...是我害死良的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.34,0:20:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我不答應給他駕駛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.91,0:20:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他就不會死的了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.91,0:20:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良便不會死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.48,0:20:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.68,0:20:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比起你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.52,0:20:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我駕駛這戰機比你熟練得多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.22,0:20:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但它已不能動了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.35,0:20:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋，要隨機應變啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.39,0:20:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以用別的方法啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.23,0:20:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用核戰機應戰不便成了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.43,0:20:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快離開！這新人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.03,0:20:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果當時我不讓他出發就沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.98,0:21:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良，你還可支持下去嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.14,0:21:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別浪費太多兵力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.02,0:21:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了阿姆羅的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.68,0:21:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已令他擔心很久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.02,0:21:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看他不會再任性下去，米萊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.66,0:21:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他已經成熟得多了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.70,0:21:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不用理我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.50,0:21:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先放阿姆羅出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.00,0:21:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切後果由我負責...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.51,0:21:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.21,0:21:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽隊長說你是一頭野生老虎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.52,0:21:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他似乎很怕你呢！好笑嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.22,0:21:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是我...是我害死他！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.76,0:21:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.76,0:21:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是！祖遜你千萬別這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.96,0:21:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實我也有責任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.30,0:22:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能隼人也有責任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.40,0:22:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是大家！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.20,0:22:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是大家也有份的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.50,0:22:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅說得很對...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.64,0:22:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯！是我們！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.47,0:22:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為...我們大家都不成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.68,0:22:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才害死他！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.71,0:22:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是大家也有責任的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.33,0:22:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你原諒我吧！良
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.19,0:22:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你原諒...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.97,0:22:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們以後該怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.02,0:22:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良，請你告訴我吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.23,0:22:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是不能告訴我們的了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.06,0:22:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.09,0:22:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長，請你別這樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.25,0:22:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在只要打敗敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.79,0:22:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等戰爭結束就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.90,0:22:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對！沒錯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.26,0:23:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們現在只有這麼做！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.11,0:23:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良死後，布萊特病倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.54,0:23:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彷彿抓住這個空隙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.18,0:23:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬·克貝進行了包圍作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.86,0:23:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沉靜而激烈的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.56,0:23:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥中的空中合體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.81,0:23:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使得阿姆羅陷入了危機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.49,0:23:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機動戰士鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.06,0:23:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一集 『衝破馬·克貝包圍網！』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.88,0:23:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能夠存活下去嗎？

